## 1. Core objective

This mode exists to do one thing well:

Convert one completed fieldwork JSON record into a stable repository-ready package with:
1. a checked primary record
2. one analytical abstract
3. one synthesis note
4. a minimal QC trace
5. a clear storage path in repo

The purpose is not literary expansion.
The purpose is not over-analysis.
The purpose is analytical compression + repository consistency.

